title: Escape Masters

creator: CASUAL AZUR GAMES
descriptionHtml:
Can you create a perfect escape plan and help the other escapist to get out? Can you escape from the police and boring prison life? Try out Escape Masters – one of the funniest brain games. Think of how to escape room and get out of jail. Show who is the best among cops and robbers! Say ‘goodbye jail’!

Escaping prison has never been so fun!
– Freaky traps – real brain test
– Cool and trendy skins
– Hella cool wheels
– Sick mansions for big boys

Use logic to move people carefully and make a perfect escape. Dig the right way to escape away and enjoy freedom. Show everyone that you can't be held within bars! Carry out a perfect jailbreak, escape right now!
descriptionShort: They can't lock you up!
